conversation.content: Hi there! I'm Jake, I work in software development.
What brings you to this networking event today?
I'm here to connect with other professionals in the tech industry. I'm particularly interested in AI and machine learning applications. What about you?
I've been working on some machine learning projects myself. What got you started in AI?
That's great to hear! I started with a research project in natural language processing during my master's program. It's fascinating how the field has evolved. Are you on LinkedIn?
I'd love to connect on LinkedIn to keep in touch and share insights about ML projects. My profile has some of my recent work.
Actually, I need to catch up with a colleague I just spotted. Would you excuse me for a moment?
Of course, no problem. It was great talking with you about AI and your experiences.
Likewise! It was nice meeting you. Enjoy the rest of the event.
Thanks, you too! Looking forward to connecting online.
